Annie Jones (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annie_Jones_(actress) 0 Annie Jones (born Annika Jancso 13 January 1967 in Adelaide) is an Australian actress, known for her roles as Jess Campbell in Sons and Daughters and as Jane Harris in the soap opera Neighbours. She has won two Logie Awards.
